strings: <se_def>The prince Carlos: Where do you think you are going? - I say.
<se_def>The prince Carlos: It was a royal hunt in eastern Aragon. I misunderstood you, you stupid and helpless!
<se_def>The prince Carlos: <leader> Greetings! If you go north from here, you won't be able to get to the royal hunting grounds!
<se_def>The prince Carlos: Eastern Kingdoms Hunting Lands! Don't be hard, take me with you!
